com.facebook.buck.cli.bootstrapper.filesystem

Class BuckFileSystem

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.nio.file.FileSystem
      • com.facebook.buck.cli.bootstrapper.filesystem.BuckFileSystem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public class BuckFileSystem
extends FileSystem
    File system implementation that returns memory footprint optimized Path object. It delegates other calls to Java-default file system.
